    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You have seriously got to see this beauty. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, kept tucked away in the garage and treated like royalty. Honestly, it looks and drives just like it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor\u2014not a single scratch or smudge in sight! It even still has that fresh new-car smell. I\u2019m looking for a new home for it where it\u2019ll be just as loved. It's a total dream to drive, so come take a look!",
      "price": 44900.0,
