    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. The S54 power plant remains in peak mechanical health, having undergone a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rod bearing replacement for preventative longevity. The throttle response from the individual throttle bodies is instantaneous, feeding through a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission to a tight limited-slip differential. The chassis is structurally flawless, with the rear subframe fully inspected and reinforced. Finished in Alpine White over a preserved Nappa leather interior, this example exhibits zero oxidative wear on the undercarriage and retains factory-spec suspension geometry for an unfiltered, analog driving experience. A true investment-grade specimen.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
