    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive excellence. This vehicle is in showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage since day one. The exterior features the original factory paint, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating that offers a deep, mirror-like finish without a single swirl mark or stone chip. Inside, the cabin remains in a 'time-capsule' state; the premium leather upholstery still retains its factory-fresh scent, and every surface\u2014from the dashboard to the door cards\u2014is completely free of wear, fading, or blemishes. Mechanically, the car is flawless, backed by a comprehensive, documented service history from authorized dealerships. It has never seen rain, let alone snow, and has been driven sparingly only on clear weekend afternoons. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to acquire a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Includes all original keys, manuals, and a custom-fitted car cover.",
